sentences: David Lee Shankle (born March 7, 1962) is an American guitarist.
Shankle was the guitarist for the band Manowar from 1989 to 1995 and he played on the album The Triumph of Steel.
He was previously a member of the band Paradoxx with whom he appeared on the Chicago Class Of '85 compilation contributing the song "Night Ryder".
